My Configuration file is called Pong_config.txt
The file lists each value as the variable name followed by a single space and then the number.
cwidth is court width
cheight is court height
ballsize is the size of the ball
pspeed is the speed at which the paddles move
dx is the speed of the ball in the x direction
dy is the speed of the ball in the y direction
maxbs is the maximum speed that the ball can travel in either the x or y direction
minbs is the minimum speed that the ball can travel in either the x or y direction
